                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Replace the VSS (refer to Inspecting and Adjusting the Vehicle Speed Sensor.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>2.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Off</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Use test leads and measure resistance between VSS sensor terminals.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
